  "title": "Trendy 6 bar low pressure shot",
  "author": "Decent",
  "notes": "Some lightly roasted espresso beans smell great but resist being well extracted into a drink.  The solution can be to lower the pressure to 6 bar. Try this technique if you're having trouble with a particularly sophisticated lightly roasted bean.",
